  <brief_title>Ig NextGen 10% in Idiopathic Thrombocytopenic Purpura (ITP) Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Single-arm, Open Label, Multi-centre Study Evaluating the Efficacy and Safety of Ig NexGen 10% in Patients With Idiopathic Thrombocytopenic Purpura (ITP)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
